create table UpdateCycle (
ID int null,
DO_NO varchar(50) not null,
StandCycle int null,
MaxInjectionCycle int null,
MinInjectionCycle int null,
UpdateStandCycle int null,
UpdateMaxInjectionCycle int null,
UpdateMinInjectionCycle int null,
UpdateTime datetime null,
CreateTime datetime null,
UpdateEmployee varchar(20) null,
constraint PK_UPDATECYCLE primary key (DO_NO)
)
